features: 🎥【90° Design – Shorter Side Facing Screen】This 4K Mini HDMI to HDMI cable boasts a 90-degree elbow for snug fit in tight spaces, preventing bending and increasing durability, Perfect for a tidy office environment. Note: Available in two models; select this one if the shorter side of your device's mini hdmi port faces the screen.

📷【Bi-Directional Mini HDMI Transmission】: ★NOTE★ Please make sure your device has mini HDMI port, NOT micro HDMI or micro USB.Supports mini HDMI to HDMI & HDMI to mini HDMI. It can help you to stream audio and video from a camera, camcorders, tablet, graphics cards, or laptop through the mini HDMI Port to your HDTV or projector with HDMI port.

🎥【Fit for Mini HDMI Devices】: Compatible with Raspberry Pi Zero, Pi zero w, Lenovo ThinkPad Yoga 12 inch laptop, NUC barebones desktop PC, Geforce GT 430 graphics card, video card, camcorder, Nvidia Shield K1 tablet, pico projector, Sony HDR-XR500, Nikon D3200, Nikon D810, DSLR and more canon cameras with a mini HDMI port.
📷【4K@60HZ UHD Visual Feast】: Fully supports 4K resolution at 60Hz and backward compatible with full HD 1080P video to external HDTV display, monitor, or projector.

🎥【HDMI 2.0 Full Compliance】: Supports for an HDMI Audio Return Channel (ARC), HDMI Ethernet Channel (HEC), 48-bit color depth, 32 channel audio, Dolby True HD 7.1 audio, and 3D video; HDCP compliant for viewing content protected video; Category 2 HDMI cables support an increased bandwidth up to 18 Gbps.

📷【Stable Transmission】: 30AWG tinned copper conductors provide this mini HDMI cord with superior conductivity. Triple shieldings effectively protect against EMI interference, ensuring more stable signal transmission. With gold plated connectors, this high-speed mini HDMI cable offers you a longer lifespan.
